text: Rebecca Chircop (born 6 July 1988) is a Maltese former footballer who played as a defender. She has been a member of the Malta women's national team. ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Maltese women's footballers Category:Malta women's international footballers Category:Mosta F.C. players Category:Birkirkara F.C.
